-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- A.R.C.H. Story NPC System
-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- Hardcoded archetypes for vanilla story NPCs. These are locked — creation
-- packs cannot redefine them. Packs add content (dialogs, tasks) by
-- referencing the archetype ID: story_<profile_name>
--
-- To add a new NPC: add the profile name to the appropriate block below.
-- To add a new block type: create a new table + register it in BLOCKS.
-- NPC Blocks — one list per role
-- ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
-- Each entry is the vanilla profile_name (from character_desc XML).
-- Archetype ID is auto-generated: "story_" .. profile_name

